	* CMake/Modules/FindENet.cmake: Fixed ENet status always being set to
	"found".
	* src/configuration.cpp, src/utils/xml.h, src/resources/mapreader.cpp,
	src/resources/spritedef.cpp, src/resources/monsterdb.cpp,
